name: What The Funk Window Decal
description: This decal will look great on your car! Take WTF with you, wherever you go! and… FREE SHIPPING!!! Make sure surface is very clean before applying. Apply to window, rub with a hard edge (for example, use the edge of your credit card) to be sure decal has no air bubbles. Slowly peel the paper off. Ta-da! An awesome decal on your car!
